snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [273] Bionicle (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

This Lego game is named simply Bionicle, not to be confused with another GBA game called LEGO Bionicle!

You never know where you'll end up with those isometric platforms. Controls are also terrible. And if that's not enough you have to finish the game twice (as Toa and Toa Nuva) in order to complete it.

00:00:46 Toa
01:31:40 Toa Nuva -
